Introduction

Haeyoon is a South Korean singer formerly under FNC Entertainment and FNC W. She was a member and the Leader and Main Vocalist of the South Korean girl group Cherry Bullet.

In 2018, Haeyoon appeared as a contestant un Mnet survival "Produce 48". She was eliminated in the finale with her final rank being 19th.

On January 21, 2019, she made her official debut as a member of the South Korean girl group Cherry Bullet with the single mini album "Let's Play Cherry Bullet" with "Q & A" serving as the title track.
